核心思路：分层生成 + 约束传播
把生成过程拆成 3 层，而不是一次性全部随机：

L1：锚点层	gender, grade, university_tier, field, family_income_level	独立概率抽样（代码执行）
L2：推理层	major, monthly_budget, phone.model, consumption_psychology, life_goal, living_situation	根据 L1 做条件概率抽样（代码执行，但带条件分支）
L3：润色层	hobbies, social_platform, primary_stressor, phone_usage 各项	交给大模型，但给足上下文约束（Prompt 控制）

L1 锚点层	严格执行概率分布，保证基础多样性	代码随机抽样
gender, grade, hometown, university_tier, academic_performance, field,
family_income_level, device_stack, mbti, relationship, hobbies

L2 推理层	基于 L1 做条件概率偏移，实现弱关联	代码条件抽样	
age, major, city_tier, monthly_budget, living_situation, phone (brand+model), purchase_priority,
life_goal

L3 润色层
university, behavior中的social_network_size, screen_time, phone_usage, social_platform, ai_usage,
primary_stressor, consumption_psychology
